    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and structural subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains sharp with updated bushings and a responsive suspension geometry. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is robust, providing the linear torque curve and balanced handling dynamics synonymous with the M-division's peak analog era.",
