    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for car that performs beautifully. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch, consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and free of odors; the leather upholstery is supple, showing only light creasing on the driver's seat bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the touchscreen navigation system, is in full working order. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and brake pad replacement just 2,000 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission is responsive, and the tires provide excellent grip with plenty of life left. This is an honest, solid vehicle that has been maintained with pride.",
